@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_sjspii(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = (0.03 - (v1 - wp.exp(v0 + 0.60)))
    v0 = (v0 / wp.sin(wp.exp(v0 + 0.89)))
    tmp = (wp.cos((v0 + 0.98 - v0 + 0.45)) - (wp.abs(v2 + 0.77) + v2))
    v2 = (0.68 - (wp.abs(v0 + 0.33) + tmp))
    tmp = ((wp.sin(v0 + 0.72) - tmp) / wp.abs((v1 + 0.09 - v1 + 0.28)))
    v1 = tmp
    data[tid] = v0
